---
title: Matured Sirloin Steak and Wedges with Provencale Traybake and Balsamic Herby Drizzle
description: Sometimes only a showstopper recipe will do, and our sirloin steak is just that. Made with fresh provencale veggies and drizzled in balsamic herb dressing, the complex flavours perfectly match the taste of a rich sirloin steak.
